#Text=Wikinews interviews U.S. Libertarian presidential candidate Bob Jackson
#Text=Wednesday , February 13 , 2008
#Text=Wikinews
#Text=held an exclusive interview with Bob Jackson , one of the candidates for the Libertarian Party nomination for the 2008 U.S. presidential election .
#Text=Jackson , an engineer , believes that he can win the Libertarian nomination and , though it is unlikely , the White House as well .
#Text=He believes that the strength of America is based on the maximum freedom of citizens who are responsible for their actions .
#Text=" This " , he says , " is guaranteed by the Constitution and made possible by the rule of law and limited government .

column1: #Text=( (
#Text=WN
#Text=) )
#Text=:
#Text=Do you think that you have a good shot at getting the Libertarian nomination ?
#Text=If so , do you think it 's possible that you could be in the White House this time next year ?
#Text=Mr. Jackson :
#Text=I do believe that I have an excellent chance to gain the Libertarian nomination because my experience is best for governance at the federal level .
#Text=It is possible but not probable for victory at this time .

#Text=However , If the electorate finds non leader Senators from a dysfunctional government are only a choice between the lesser of two evils , and they understand the Libertarian alternative , I can be elected .
#Text=( (
#Text=WN
#Text=) )
#Text=:
#Text=There are thousands reading this right now .
#Text=What could you say to convince them to give you their vote ?
#Text=Mr. Jackson :
#Text=I believe that the strength of this country is based on the maximum freedom of the citizens who are responsible for their actions .
#Text=This is guaranteed by the constitution and made possible by the rule of law and limited government .
#Text=The government must be returned to the people and to the authority granted in the constitution .
#Text=I truly believe that , with the help of the people , I have the background and ability to the president and guide a transition to return the federal government back to the Constitution .
#Text=I am an Eagle scout .
#Text=That means that I am trustworthy , Loyal , Honest , Prepared , trained and I help others at all times .
#Text=I am responsible for my actions and I take full advantage of my personal freedoms .
#Text=That is –
#Text=I have always been a Libertarian .
#Text=I am an engineer – weigh all the facts and make the best solution that works . 100 % vrs 51 % .
#Text=I have better broad based business , citizen and community credentials than any other candidate .
#Text=I have unequalled energy and drive .
#Text=Check my web page bobjackson.org Particularly review my plans for correcting a dysfunctional government , a real energy policy and a better national defense .
